Hy2Scale - Decentralized Hysteria2 Relay Network

Features:
- Hysteria2 QUIC tunnel relay
- L2TP/IPsec VPN server
- IKEv2/MSCHAPv2 VPN server
- WireGuard VPN server
- IP/Domain routing rules engine
- TUN mode IP packet forwarding
- SOCKS5/Shadowsocks proxy
- Web management UI

Usage:
1. Access http://<device-ip>:<web-port>/scale/ after installation
2. Default username: admin, set password on first login
3. Add relay nodes on the Nodes page
4. Add VPN users on the Users page
5. Enable L2TP/IKEv2/WireGuard on the Proxies page
